<h1 class="ds-title">The <em>Curie</em> design system</h1>
<p class="ds-lede">Curie is ZoomRx's dark-themed medical-content platform for healthcare professionals. This site documents its visual language — tokens, components, and reusable page layouts (desktop + responsive) — generated directly from the design-system package, so it can never drift from the code it describes.</p>

