<h2 class="ds-section">For machines as well as people</h2>
<p>Everything on this site is generated from two structured files, published for AI agents and plugins to consume directly: <a href="/api/tokens.json" style="color: var(--color-purple-light)">tokens.json</a> and <a href="/api/components-manifest.json" style="color: var(--color-purple-light)">components-manifest.json</a>. The git repository is the canonical source; this site and those endpoints are derived output of version {{ site.version }}.</p>
